## Bug reports

If you found a bug, or this mod crashed your game. I'll appreciate if you could report a bug or a crash to me either on [issue tracker](<?php echo $links[$project]['github'] ?>/issues/), on PM or on [Twitter](<?php echo $links['twitter'] ?>). Please, make sure to attach a crash log ([pastebin](http://pastebin.com) please) and description of a bug or crash and the way to reproduce it. Thanks!